@node history "History"

1.0	First release of DTU.

1.1	- Lower amount of retries in the block search now, unformatted
	  disks will now read faster.
	- Removed DOS disk initialisation. If no disk is inserted on
	  startup, the drive will not bump the head anymore.
	- Not found blocks will not be re-read anymore.
	- SCPU fix.

@endnode
